main event: A resident in Elmhurst, Illinois observed a strange, flickering light in the sky that appeared to be a UFO over a 30-day period in 1965.
interesting points: The object appeared to be a bright, flickering light that would fade in and out.
The object was sighted in the west, about 45 degrees above the horizon.
The object seemed to descend and then move across the sky, shaking from side to side.
The witness reported that the TV in their house was going off and on during the sighting.
The object was visible for 30-60 minutes on multiple occasions over a 30-day period.
sighted object: a bright, flickering light in the sky
